{
  "script_id": "graph-coloring",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "给一张地图上色，你想让相邻的两个国家颜色不同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "问题来了：最少需要准备几种颜色，才能涂完整张地图？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.56,
      "size": 40896,
      "text": "把每个区域看成一个点，相邻区域之间连一条线，地图就变成了一张图。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "constraint",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "constraint-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/constraint-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.45,
      "size": 39168,
      "text": "图着色的唯一规则是：任何一条边连接的两个节点，颜色必须不同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "constraint",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "constraint-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/constraint-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.39,
      "size": 38304,
      "text": "如果两个相邻节点涂成了同色，这条边就成了冲突边，我们把它标红。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "constraint",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "constraint-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/constraint-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.68,
      "size": 26928,
      "text": "目标是用尽量少的颜色，让所有边都不冲突。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "greedy",
      "line_id": "greedy-1",
      "filename": "greedy-greedy-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/greedy-greedy-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.78,
      "size": 28512,
      "text": "一个简单办法是贪心法：按顺序处理每个节点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "greedy",
      "line_id": "greedy-2",
      "filename": "greedy-greedy-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/greedy-greedy-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "给当前节点挑一个还没被它邻居用过的、编号最小的颜色。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "greedy",
      "line_id": "greedy-3",
      "filename": "greedy-greedy-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/greedy-greedy-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "贪心很快，但用到的颜色不一定最少，答案还和节点顺序有关。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "chromatic",
      "line_id": "chrom-1",
      "filename": "chromatic-chrom-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/chromatic-chrom-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "一张图能被合法着色所需的最少颜色数，叫做它的色数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "chromatic",
      "line_id": "chrom-2",
      "filename": "chromatic-chrom-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/chromatic-chrom-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.65,
      "size": 42480,
      "text": "要求出色数，可以用回溯法：从一种颜色开始逐步增加，直到能涂满为止。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "chromatic",
      "line_id": "chrom-3",
      "filename": "chromatic-chrom-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/chromatic-chrom-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "著名的四色定理说：任何平面地图，四种颜色一定够用。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "切换不同的图，看看贪心着色分别用了几种颜色。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "再对比回溯法求出的真正色数，感受两者的差距。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "图着色要在相邻不同色的约束下，用最少的颜色涂满全图。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "贪心法快而不一定最优，回溯法能求出真正的色数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "graph-coloring",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/graph-coloring/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "从地图到调度，图着色无处不在，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 35.989999999999995,
  "total_size": 576144
}